---
---
    <header class="hero" id="top">
      <div>
        <div class="hero-meta">
          <span class="mark">AGYL</span>
          <span class="div">/</span>
          <span>The operating layer for AI-ready data</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="hero-title">Your AI is only as smart as <em>the records</em> it reads from.<br>AGYL is the <em>operating layer</em> that makes them <em>AI-ready</em>.</h1>

        <div class="hero-grid">
          <div class="hero-copy">
            <p>Foundation models keep getting more capable every quarter, and more interchangeable. They are becoming infrastructure. <b>The bottleneck is no longer the model. It is the records the model reads from, which live in many systems and rarely agree.</b></p>
            <p>AGYL is the operating layer above that infrastructure. It reads across your systems, decides what is true about every record that matters, holds the evidence behind every value, and hands AI-ready records to whatever reads them next — a copilot, an agent, a workflow, a person. <b>Your standards govern it. Your team approves the calls that carry risk. Everything built on top belongs to you.</b></p>
            <div class="hero-cta-row">
              <a href="#close" class="btn btn-primary">See it on your data <span class="arr">→</span></a>
              <a href="#what-you-get" class="btn btn-ghost">How AGYL works</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-vis">
            <div class="vh">
              <span>RESOLUTION · LIVE FEED</span>
              <span class="live">RUNNING</span>
            </div>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 540 460" role="img" aria-label="A record resolving live inside the operating layer">
              <defs>
                <style>
                  .hp-cap{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9.5px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.16em;fill:rgba(245,244,241,.5);text-transform:uppercase}
                  .hp-cap-ink{fill:#F5F4F1}
                  .hp-h{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;fill:#F5F4F1;letter-spacing:-.005em}
                  .hp-lbl{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10.5px;font-weight:500;fill:#F5F4F1;letter-spacing:.02em}
                  .hp-mute{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;font-weight:400;fill:rgba(245,244,241,.5);letter-spacing:.02em}
                  .hp-mute-ink{fill:rgba(245,244,241,.78)}
                  .hp-num{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:30px;font-weight:300;fill:#F5F4F1;letter-spacing:-.025em}
                  .hp-warn{fill:#C9A875}
                  .hp-good{fill:#7A9A7F}
                  .hp-bar{
                    transform-origin:left center;
                    animation:hpBar 2.4s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.3,1) backwards;
                  }
                  @keyframes hpBar{ from{transform:scaleX(0);} to{transform:scaleX(1);} }
                  .hp-rfade{ animation:hpFade 1s ease-out backwards; }
                  @keyframes hpFade{ from{opacity:0; transform:translateY(4px);} to{opacity:1;} }
                  .hp-cursor{ animation:hpBlink 1.2s steps(1) infinite; }
                  @keyframes hpBlink{ 50%{opacity:0;} }
                  .hp-stream{ stroke-dasharray:4 6; animation:hpStream 2.2s linear infinite; }
                  @keyframes hpStream{ to{stroke-dashoffset:-60;} }
                </style>
              </defs>

              <!-- ============ TOP: SOURCES (modern stack mix) ============ -->
              <text class="hp-cap" x="0" y="14">3 SOURCES RECONCILED · UPDATED 2s AGO</text>

              <!-- Source 1 -->
              <g class="hp-rfade" style="animation-delay:0s">
                <rect x="0" y="26" width="540" height="38" fill="rgba(201,168,117,.08)" stroke="rgba(201,168,117,.32)"/>
                <text class="hp-cap hp-warn" x="14" y="44">SALESFORCE · CRM</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl" x="14" y="58">Halsey, Inc.</text>
                <text class="hp-mute" x="526" y="50" text-anchor="end">ARR $48,000</text>
                <text class="hp-mute" x="526" y="64" text-anchor="end">last edit: Mar 4</text>
              </g>

              <!-- Source 2 -->
              <g class="hp-rfade" style="animation-delay:.3s">
                <rect x="0" y="72" width="540" height="38" fill="rgba(201,168,117,.08)" stroke="rgba(201,168,117,.32)"/>
                <text class="hp-cap hp-warn" x="14" y="90">SLACK · #revenue-ops thread</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl" x="14" y="104">"Halsey just confirmed $52.4K Q1 invoice"</text>
                <text class="hp-mute" x="526" y="96" text-anchor="end">m.chen · 2d ago</text>
                <text class="hp-mute" x="526" y="110" text-anchor="end">attachment: invoice.pdf</text>
              </g>

              <!-- Source 3 -->
              <g class="hp-rfade" style="animation-delay:.6s">
                <rect x="0" y="118" width="540" height="38" fill="rgba(201,168,117,.08)" stroke="rgba(201,168,117,.32)"/>
                <text class="hp-cap hp-warn" x="14" y="136">NOTION · Account brief, Halsey</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl" x="14" y="150">Halsey Industrial Supply</text>
                <text class="hp-mute" x="526" y="142" text-anchor="end">renewal: "April"</text>
                <text class="hp-mute" x="526" y="156" text-anchor="end">owner: J. Morales</text>
              </g>

              <!-- ============ ARROW DOWN: RESOLVING ============ -->
              <g class="hp-rfade" style="animation-delay:.95s">
                <line x1="270" y1="170" x2="270" y2="200" stroke="rgba(245,244,241,.5)" stroke-width="1" class="hp-stream"/>
                <path d="M264 196 L270 204 L276 196" fill="none" stroke="rgba(245,244,241,.5)" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                <text class="hp-cap hp-cap-ink" x="270" y="186" text-anchor="middle">RESOLVING</text>
              </g>

              <!-- ============ MIDDLE: RESOLVED RECORD ============ -->
              <g class="hp-rfade" style="animation-delay:1.2s">
                <!-- Card frame with subtle inner glow -->
                <rect x="0" y="216" width="540" height="186" fill="rgba(122,154,127,.10)" stroke="rgba(122,154,127,.55)" stroke-width="1"/>

                <!-- Top bar inside card -->
                <text class="hp-cap hp-good" x="14" y="236">RESOLVED RECORD · CUSTOMER MASTER</text>
                <text class="hp-cap" x="526" y="236" text-anchor="end">CONFIDENCE 0.96</text>

                <line x1="14" y1="246" x2="526" y2="246" stroke="rgba(245,244,241,.10)"/>

                <!-- The resolved record body -->
                <text class="hp-h" x="14" y="270">Halsey, Inc.</text>
                <text class="hp-mute" x="14" y="286">d/b/a Halsey Industrial Supply · 7-yr customer</text>

                <!-- key facts grid -->
                <text class="hp-mute hp-mute-ink" x="14" y="318">True ARR</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl" x="180" y="318">$52,400</text>

                <text class="hp-mute hp-mute-ink" x="14" y="338">Active contract</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl" x="180" y="338">MSA-2024-118</text>

                <text class="hp-mute hp-mute-ink" x="14" y="358">Renewal</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl hp-warn" x="180" y="358">Apr 14 · 47d out</text>

                <text class="hp-mute hp-mute-ink" x="290" y="318">Owner</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl" x="396" y="318">J. Morales</text>

                <text class="hp-mute hp-mute-ink" x="290" y="338">MFN clause</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl" x="396" y="338">Yes · ¶ 7.2</text>

                <text class="hp-mute hp-mute-ink" x="290" y="358">Linked records</text>
                <text class="hp-lbl" x="396" y="358">4 SKUs · 1 asset</text>

                <line x1="14" y1="375" x2="526" y2="375" stroke="rgba(245,244,241,.10)"/>
                <text class="hp-cap hp-good" x="14" y="392">DEPLOYED · CRM + SALES + RENEWAL CALENDAR</text>
              </g>

              <!-- ============ BOTTOM: LIVE PROGRESS ============ -->
              <g class="hp-rfade" style="animation-delay:1.6s">
                <text class="hp-cap" x="0" y="426">EVIDENCE CHAIN</text>
                <text class="hp-cap" x="540" y="426" text-anchor="end">5 OF 5 CITED · 1 APPROVAL APPLIED</text>

                <!-- progress bar -->
                <rect x="0" y="436" width="540" height="2" fill="rgba(245,244,241,.10)"/>
                <rect x="0" y="436" width="540" height="2" fill="#F5F4F1" class="hp-bar-loop"/>
              </g>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-foot">
          <div>What it is<b>AI infrastructure</b></div>
          <div>Specifically<b>The operating layer above the model</b></div>
          <div>What it does<b>Makes your records AI-ready</b></div>
          <div>Who owns it<b>You do, by architecture</b></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- WHAT AGYL IS -->
